\c 9
\s UAroni unikela iminikelo
\p
\v 1 Kwasekusithi ngosuku lwesificaminwembili\x + Hez. 43.27.\x* uMozisi wabiza oAroni lamadodana akhe labadala bakoIsrayeli.
\v 2 Wathi kuAroni: Zithathele ithole, inkonyana yenkomo, libe ngumnikelo wesono\x + Eks. 29.1. Levi 4.3; 8.14.\x*, lenqama ibe ngumnikelo wokutshiswa\x + 8.18.\x*, okungelasici, ukusondeze eN\nd kosi\nd*ni.
\v 3 Lebantwaneni bakoIsrayeli uzakhuluma uthi: Thathani izinyane lembuzi libe ngumnikelo wesono\x + 4.23. Ezra 6.17.\x*, lethole, lewundlu, abe lomnyaka owodwa, angelasici, abe ngumnikelo wokutshiswa,
\v 4 lenkabi lenqama zibe yiminikelo yokuthula\x + 3.1,12.\x*, zihlatshwe phambi kweN\nd kosi\nd*, lomnikelo wokudla oxubene lamafutha\x + 9.17; 2.4.\x*; ngoba lamuhla iN\nd kosi\nd* izabonakala kini\x + 9.6,23. Eks. 29.43.\x*.
\p
\v 5 Basebethatha lokho uMozisi akulayayo bakuletha phambi kwethente lenhlangano; lenhlangano yonke yasondela, yema phambi kweN\nd kosi\nd*.
\v 6 UMozisi wasesithi: Le into iN\nd kosi\nd* elilaye ngayo lizayenza; lenkazimulo yeN\nd kosi\nd* izabonakala kini.
\v 7 UMozisi wasesithi kuAroni: Sondela elathini, wenze umnikelo wakho wesono\x + 4.3; 1.3. Heb. 5.3; 7.27; 9.7.\x* lomnikelo wakho wokutshiswa\x + 4.3; 1.3. Heb. 5.3; 7.27; 9.7.\x*, uzenzele wena inhlawulo yokuthula lokwabantu; ubususenza umnikelo wabantu\x + 4.16,20; Heb. 5.1.\x*, ubenzele inhlawulo yokuthula, njengokulaya kweN\nd kosi\nd*.
\p
\v 8 UAroni wasesondela elathini, walihlaba ithole lomnikelo wesono owawungowakhe.
\v 9 Amadodana kaAroni aseletha igazi kuye\x + 4.6; 8.15.\x*, wasegxamuza umunwe wakhe egazini, walifaka phezu kwempondo zelathi\x + 4.7.\x*, legazi walithululela kungaphansi yelathi;
\v 10 kodwa amahwahwa\x + 3.4; 8.16.\x*, lezinso, lamahwahwa esibindi omnikelo wesono wakutshisa elathini, njengalokho iN\nd kosi\nd* imlayile uMozisi\x + 4.8.\x*.
\v 11 Kodwa inyama lesikhumba wakutshisa ngomlilo ngaphandle kwenkamba\x + 4.11; 8.17.\x*.
\v 12 Wasehlaba umnikelo wokutshiswa; lamadodana kaAroni amnika igazi, waselifafaza phezu kwelathi inhlangothi zonke\x + 1.5; 8.19; 9.2,7.\x*.
\v 13 Amnika lomnikelo wokutshiswa ngezitho zawo lenhloko\x + 8.20.\x*; wasekutshisa phezu kwelathi.
\v 14 Wagezisa imibilini lemilenze\x + 8.21.\x*, wayitshisa phezu komnikelo wokutshiswa elathini.
\p
\v 15 Wasesondeza umnikelo wabantu\x + 9.3,7; Heb.2.17; 5.3.\x*, wathatha impongo yomnikelo wesono eyayingeyabantu, wayihlaba, wayinikela yaba ngumnikelo wesono\x + Eks.29.36; Levi 6.26; 8.15; 14.49,52.\x*, njengowokuqala.
\v 16 Wasondeza umnikelo wokutshiswa, wawulungisa njengokwesimiso.
\v 17 Wasondeza umnikelo wokudla\x + 9.4; 2.1,2.\x*, wagcwalisa isandla sakhe ngokwawo, wakutshisa phezu kwelathi, ngaphandle komnikelo wokutshiswa wekuseni\x + Eks. 29.38,39. Gen. 26.1. Nani 6.21. Dute. 4.35.\x*.
\v 18 Wahlaba inkabi lenqama zibe ngumhlatshelo weminikelo yokuthula\x + 3.1,12,16.\x* owawungowabantu; lamadodana kaAroni amnika igazi, owalifafaza phezu kwelathi inhlangothi zonke.
\v 19 Lamahwahwa enkabi lawenqama, umsila ononileyo, le\add danga\add* elisibekelayo, lezinso, lamahwahwa esibindi\x + 3.3,9,14; 4.8; 7.3.\x*,
\v 20 asebeka amahwahwa phezu kwezifuba; wasetshisa amahwahwa elathini;
\v 21 kodwa izifuba lomlenze wokunene uAroni wakuzunguza kwaba ngumnikelo wokuzunguzwa phambi kweN\nd kosi\nd*\x + 7.30-34. Eks. 29.24,26.\x*, njengokulaya kukaMozisi.
\p
\v 22 UAroni wasephakamisela isandla sakhe ebantwini, wababusisa\x + Nani 6.23-27. Dute. 21.5.\x*. Wehla ekunikeleni umnikelo wesono lomnikelo wokutshiswa leminikelo yokuthula.
\v 23 UMozisi loAroni basebengena ethenteni lenhlangano; baphuma bababusisa abantu, lenkazimulo yeN\nd kosi\nd* yabonakala kubo bonke abantu\x + 9.4,6. Nani 14.10; 16.19,42.\x*.
\v 24 Kwasekuphuma umlilo uvela phambi kweN\nd kosi\nd*\x + Gen. 4.4; Hlu. 6.21; 1 Kho. 18.38; 2 Lan. 7.1. Hlab. 20.3.\x*, watshisa phezu kwelathi umnikelo wokutshiswa lamahwahwa. Bonke abantu bathi bekubona lokhu bamemeza\x + Ezra 3.11.\x*, bawa ngobuso babo\x + 1 Kho. 18.39. 2 Lan. 7.3.\x*.